                <h1>Dear Noah: Putting balance into practice</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/8f8806da-3725-41c6-a9cc-0ef30563e3c1.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;&quot;Maybe&#x20;when&#x20;I&#x20;grow&#x20;back&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;spring,&#x20;construction&#x20;will&#x20;be&#x20;done.&#x20;Lol...I&#x27;m&#x20;a&#x20;funny&#x20;tree.&quot;&#x20;&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>"Maybe when I grow back in the spring, construction will be done. Lol...I'm a funny tree." &nbsp;</p>

